OL,7,FMADRID ` Thousands of British expats in
OL,8,FSpain were celebrating after the
OL,9,FSpanish government announced they could
OL,10,Fuse their licences in the country, and
OL,11,Fwill not have to retake their tests.
OL,13,FThe Spanish cabinet announced Britons
OL,14,Fcould get back on the road from
OL,15,FThursday but had six months to exchange
OL,16,Ftheir licences for Spanish ones.
OL,18,FIt ended 10 months of diplomatic
OL,19,Fwrangling between Britain and Spain
OL,20,Fover the issue, which has angered many
OL,21,Fexpats who have been left stranded.
OL,3,CSpain finally announces British expats
OL,4,Ccan use UK driving licences in the
